'''准地铁'''（{{lang-en|premetro}}）一般是指有些在修建过程中部分或全部路段按照[[地铁|地铁]]的水準修建的[[轻轨|轻轨]]或[[有轨电车|有轨电车]]系统。这种[[城市轨道交通系统|城市轨道交通系统]]一般通过[[隧道|隧道]]穿越市中心，以便日后升级成地铁<ref name="Antwerpen rail network is a typical premetro network">{{cite web | url=http://www.urbanrail.net/eu/be/ant/antwerpen.htm | title=Antwerpen rail network is a typical premetro network | accessdate=January 14, 2013 | archive-date=2013-04-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424164214/http://www.urbanrail.net/eu/be/ant/antwerpen.htm | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="The History of the Antwerpen Premetro Tram System (Belgium)">{{cite web | url=http://www.davidbakerphotography.com/the-history-of-the-antwerpen-premetro-tram-system-belgium | title=The History of the Antwerpen Premetro Tram System (Belgium) | accessdate=2013-04-22 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130808030445/http://www.davidbakerphotography.com/the-history-of-the-antwerpen-premetro-tram-system-belgium | archivedate=2013-08-08 }}</ref>。因为修建隧道造价不菲，有些准地铁未能顺利升级成为地铁，比如[[瑞典|瑞典]][[哥德堡|哥德堡]][[市郊|郊区]]的部分[[轨道交通|轨道交通]]线路、英国[[利物浦|利物浦]]的[[默西塞德铁路|默西塞德铁路]]和[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]的城市铁路系统。

